measurements.description:
Eleven flowers on two 45-cm inflorescences;
	 sepals yellow-green, bronze veins;
	 petals yellow-green, bronze veins, brown-burgundy marking proximal three-fourths, widest at base, narrowing along petal;
	 lip white overlaid green, burgundy stripe center vein distally, additional burgundy marks each side of stripe;
	 column green-yellow, anther cap white;
	 substance medium; texture matte.
